&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/20200616_235434.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;T5 Torx&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/20200616_235450.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;plastic spudger&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;2-뒷판-분리&quot;&gt;2. 뒷판 분리&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;뒷판 나사 제거 후 내부 보드 레이아웃 상태 확인&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/20200616_235947.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Remove screw&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

