&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/20200617_001839.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;replace with new right speaker&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;5-왼쪽-스피커-교체&quot;&gt;5. 왼쪽 스피커 교체&lt;/h2&gt;

